articles.author: Jon Porter
articles.title: Nothing's Phone 2A launches March 5th but with a limited US release - The Verge
articles.description: Nothing has announced a March 5th launch date for its upcoming Phone 2A, and has confirmed that it’ll be available in the US as part of a “Developer Program.”
